{"tid":395488,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"民主女神為建制站台？麥明詩稱﹕我支持好朋友","createTime":"2017-09-10T23:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T16:42:57.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"faf9af18cd754245b18fe09bb0754f87589221ff","tid":395488,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:16:42.000Z","msg":"麥明詩面對政治議題向來敢言，當選港姐之初，就被爆曾參予雨傘運動，當日佢喺Instagram寫上﹕「天下無不傘之筵席」，被封「人民民主女神」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今日有澳門讀者爆料，指麥明詩噚日為四太梁安琪率領嘅「澳門發展新連盟」站台，為17號舉行嘅澳門立法會選舉拉票。而該黨正是澳門一個建制派政治團體，麥明詩與首次出選、四太二仔何猷亨一齊站台，仲收咗支太陽花，但讀者就覺得麥明詩對澳門嘅立法會選舉認識唔多，亦唔了解四太過去喺澳門立法會嘅公職，所以對麥明詩好失望。<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩今日回覆傳媒時否認撐建制派，純粹係支持好朋友，佢話﹕「我同猷亨認識咗好多年，人生第一次見佢咁努力同投入，好想鼓勵佢，其實我都唔知背後嘅政治立場，下次會小心啲。」《澳門日報》報道，現場介紹，麥明詩原來係何猷亨喺英國讀書時認識，仲係梁安琪幼女何超欣嘅補習老師，稱麥明詩係「路過」撐好友。據了解，麥明詩同猷亨雖然讀唔同嘅大學，但林作與猷亨既是中學同學，而在英國讀書嘅華人唔算多，大家都係當地寄宿，所以認識後會互相幫忙而成為好友。<br />\n<br />\n而四太亦似乎都好鍾意呢位「十優港姐」，前年麥明詩同四太一齊出席活動，都硬要拉埋阿仔猷亨一齊合照，未知聲稱現在係單身嘅麥明詩同猷亨有冇機會發展呢？(相關新聞﹕<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gUdpIm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gUdpIm&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=3772247a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gUdpIm</a>) <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505034791_2a80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505034791_2a80.jpg&h=ac06467c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩為四太及猷亨站台，但否認撐建制派。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033641_8f89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033641_8f89.jpg&h=40c24d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩稱是撐好友猷亨。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033642_7307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033642_7307.jpg&h=9f9f2842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033643_d295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033643_d295.jpg&h=a21190fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033645_2fb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033645_2fb7.jpg&h=9022a6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩與猷亨在17、8歲時已經認識。(網絡圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033754_3ba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033754_3ba1.jpg&h=5ec70f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前年麥明詩同四太一齊出席活動，四太拉住猷亨同麥明詩一齊影相。(資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033755_96e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033755_96e7.jpg&h=4a82f0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩同林作拍拖時，曾被影到與猷亨及當時女友陳瀅一齊去玩。(資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033756_bad0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033756_bad0.jpg&h=eaa1463a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505033757_b7cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505033757_b7cf.jpg&h=7415fe38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩曾被封「民主女神」。(網絡截圖)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170910/57192375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170910%2F57192375&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c9033e4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170910%2F57192375&h=f1b7e81b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170910/57192375</a>"},{"pid":"38a28eb6bf51efd6793aa2c2b36dc5d663cd9057","tid":395488,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70001c02fba8bbedfb2989865533ddb6390454f0","tid":395488,"uid":46688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924f8e53aa4e630016217707396dd6c22dc37c76","tid":395488,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"879b0740e42942368a52fbc6718ea853cb4635db","tid":395488,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:25:58.000Z","msg":"靠攏權貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃子華：揾食啫，犯法呀？"},{"pid":"5f763e68aa38695d814dd8ce421e8404098827a4","tid":395488,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:38:41.000Z","msg":"食完陳瀅食10A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 我揀10A"},{"pid":"378f2ac88befa517dc73e35d1c6e4f77dde4cc55","tid":395488,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:20:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01b4ec7e367fe5c757fcd5f599c6df77ad4c0789","tid":395488,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"澳門都無民主㗎啦 是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d96e61631bdc359a2b7b76746a78b06ba0502f","tid":395488,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"係我都食有錢仔啦,民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc94b360d83f8fce49d8525772ba61ec5b93f762","tid":395488,"uid":111814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"有錢佬圈子都係建制架啦，想進入圈子親建制有咩問題？"},{"pid":"ba2f5c4657646210ad24b1ff9ac06be420956a3d","tid":395488,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T23:44:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>猷亨露腩自毀形象</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170911/large/11ec1p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F11ec1p8.jpg&h=4def29dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■早前澳門受颱風「天鴿」影響，猷亨即向居民派水救災。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n四太已連任3屆澳門立法會直選議員，今次她第4次參選，就找來兒子何猷亨入候選人名單，二人更開設facebook個人專頁，大部份都是貼參與選舉活動宣傳，之前協力社區善後颱風「天鴿」的報道。<br />\n<br />\n相比四太，猷亨首次參加選舉，在專頁的內容就較為生動，不時貼相開玩笑。早前他參加完誓師大會，他貼了一張打橫瞓在梳化，露出肚腩的睡覺相，更留hashtag笑言：「咩形象都冇晒」、「post出嚟面對群眾」。另有一張，猷亨與高舉他名字紙牌的助選團合照相，他笑言：「今日，我有一刻覺得自己係偶像派。」盡顯其幽默感。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170911/large/11ec1p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F11ec1p9.jpg&h=81452943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■猷亨在fb自貼睡覺相，直言為選舉頻撲到沒時間瞓。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：唐如<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170911/20148753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170911%2F20148753&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0ada4f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170911%2F20148753&h=0a99f46c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170911/20148753</a>"},{"pid":"4578d8556ddb7549f0c6d0d373ae0ec4bb890fd2","tid":395488,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:02:22.000Z","msg":"唔知政治立場？ 咁都講得出"},{"pid":"fcf111eb327c8b86b8e447d3512b7b81aae88ca6","tid":395488,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"最醜樣就係猷亨 少少都遺傳唔到老竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011886a811e0b48f8ad7253e1181357a7b86fb7d","tid":395488,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食完陳瀅食10A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 我揀10A</blockquote><br />\n有咩爽得過喺同一個朋友圈入面食晒所有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a92035da94a5c629d1ad59b66e1cc53ccb80bae","tid":395488,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"恩客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e766766e791c95a50e7cb9cb5127f4ec681a5381","tid":395488,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"a283e00555d4b348a46092425ace0ab669ac02d1","tid":395488,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"牆頭草係咪呢種？"},{"pid":"d8549cd0f3dcfabedc5e640f16dddd7b4bf02b01","tid":395488,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:44:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>【民主女神】揚言想做特首</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170911/large/11ec1p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F11ec1p7.jpg&h=94cf3b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14年12月　撐傘運<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩09年獲十優狀元後揚言想做女特首，爭取民主。15年她當選港姐冠軍，其多番敢言被網民封民主女神。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>14年12月　撐傘運</strong><br />\n金鐘佔領區清場前，於Ig貼自拍照後留言：「天下無不傘之筵席。」照片於翌年她當選港姐冠軍後在網上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>去年8月　批越權</strong><br />\n梁天琦被選舉主任裁定立法會提名無效，麥明詩於fb留言：「一個行為越權，並加上程序不當。」暗喻選舉主任行為越權，處理提名程序亦有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>去年11月　講法治</strong><br />\n人大釋法後，麥明詩於fb節錄基本法條文，留言：「但我支持程序公義，支持法治。」對網民問：「法治？邊間茶仔有得食？」她回應：「淨係得番仁治；即係蝦仁蛋治」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今年2月　鬧七警</strong><br />\n於fb轉貼七警判刑報道，並留言：「點解打人後要坐監係不公義嘅？」又hashtag真心唔明、無論邊個打邊個都應負刑責等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170911/20148751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170911%2F20148751&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=cf1b177d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170911%2F20148751&h=a0903ce7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170911/20148751</a>"},{"pid":"065ffeb2badd71a7680a0784a3d3ce1530246438","tid":395488,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"呢種富二代,真的會為無產階級打拚嗎?"},{"pid":"0661562f74fc92ec78f8f59e56b4de06117154e4","tid":395488,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"睇黎想入豪門"},{"pid":"66c8b33502f869a9f249e8dd97f72e8ea0754f95","tid":395488,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢種富二代,真的會為無產階級打拚嗎?</blockquote><br />\n點解唔會<br />\n我地窮人 都會為有錢人賣命啦<br />\n相對架姐"},{"pid":"def25dac3a12bc8dc934dcab53be5870ebd28f7c","tid":395488,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"